'''2018年國家聯盟西區封王決勝加賽'''是[[美國職棒大聯盟|美國職棒大聯盟]]{{mlby|2018}}賽季的一場{{le|決勝加賽|one-game playoff}}，目的是從{{le|2018年科羅拉多落磯隊球季|2018 Colorado Rockies season|科羅拉多落磯隊}}和{{le|2018年洛杉磯道奇隊球季|2018 Los Angeles Dodgers season|洛杉磯道奇隊}}中決定誰在[[國家聯盟|國家聯盟]][[國家聯盟西區|西區]]封王。這場比賽舉行於2018年10月1日[[加州|加州]][[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]的[[道奇體育場|道奇體育場]]。

道奇隊最終以5比2獲勝，取得第二種子之姿晉級[[2018年國家聯盟分區賽|國聯分區賽]]，與國聯東區龍頭{{le|2018年亞特蘭大勇士隊球季|2018 Atlanta Braves season|亞特蘭大勇士隊}}交手。而洛磯隊則以客場身分，在10月2日的[[2018年國家聯盟外卡晉級賽|外卡晉級賽]]中與[[2018年國家聯盟中區封王決勝加賽|國聯中區第二]]的{{le|2018年芝加哥小熊隊球季|2018 Chicago Cubs season|芝加哥小熊隊}}對戰<ref name=usatoday>{{cite web|url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/2018/09/30/mlb-playoffs-tiebreakers-dodgers-rockies-cubs-brewers/1481842002/|title=Game 163! Historic day on tap as Dodgers-Rockies, Cubs-Brewers set for NL tiebreakers Monday|last=Lacques|first=Greg|work=USA Today|date=2018-09-30|access-date=2018-09-30|archive-date=2020-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201222111647/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/2018/09/30/mlb-playoffs-tiebreakers-dodgers-rockies-cubs-brewers/1481842002/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

這場決勝加賽將被視為兩隊正規賽季的第163場比賽，比賽中的各項數據與內容也會算入正規賽季的統計當中<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/24853543/mlb-breaking-monday-division-tiebreaker-doubleheader |title=MLB - Breaking down Monday's division tiebreaker doubleheader |publisher=Espn.com |date=2018-10-01 |access-date=2018-11-26 |archive-date=2021-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109154752/https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/24853543/mlb-breaking-monday-division-tiebreaker-doubleheader |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==背景==
[[洛杉磯道奇隊|洛杉磯道奇隊]]在{{mlby|2018}}以前已經在[[國聯西區|國聯西區]]五連霸<ref>{{cite web|last=Harding |first=Thomas |url=https://www.mlb.com/news/rockies-play-dodgers-in-nl-west-tiebreaker/c-296662686 |title=Rockies to play Dodgers in NL West tiebreaker |publisher=MLB.com |date=2018-05-24 |access-date=2018-10-01}}</ref>。而[[科羅拉多落磯隊|科羅拉多落磯隊]]則是在前一年以[[外卡|外卡]]身分晉級[[美國職棒大聯盟季後賽|季後賽]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Acquavella |first=Katherine |url=https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/rockies-clinch-playoff-berth-by-beating-nationals-magic-number-two-for-nl-west-title/ |title=Rockies clinch playoff berth by beating Nationals, magic number two for NL West title |publisher=CBSSports.com |date=2018-09-28 |access-date=2018-10-02 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109021105/https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/rockies-clinch-playoff-berth-by-beating-nationals-magic-number-two-for-nl-west-title/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，儘管這是他們第五度在季後賽出線，但他們卻從未在分區封王過<ref>{{cite web |last=Acquavella |first=Katherine |url=https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/rockies-clinch-playoff-berth-by-beating-nationals-magic-number-two-for-nl-west-title/ |title=Rockies clinch playoff berth by beating Nationals, magic number two for NL West title |publisher=CBSSports.com |date=2018-09-29 |access-date=2018-11-26 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109021105/https://www.cbssports.com/mlb/news/rockies-clinch-playoff-berth-by-beating-nationals-magic-number-two-for-nl-west-title/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

道奇隊和落磯隊在2018年正規賽季結束時以的勝率{{winning percentage|91|71|record=y}}並列分區第一，因此需要進行一場決勝加賽<ref name=usatoday/>。由於[[芝加哥小熊隊|芝加哥小熊隊]]和[[密爾瓦基釀酒人隊|密爾瓦基釀酒人隊]]也在[[國家聯盟中區|國家聯盟中區]]並列第一，他們也打了場[[2018年國家聯盟中區封王決勝加賽|決勝加賽]]，這意味著[[美國職棒大聯盟|大聯盟]]將進行史上第一次的單年兩場決勝加賽<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/24853543/mlb-breaking-monday-division-tiebreaker-doubleheader |title=MLB - Breaking down Monday's division tiebreaker doubleheader |work=ESPN |access-date=2018-10-02 |archive-date=2021-01-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210109154752/https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/24853543/mlb-breaking-monday-division-tiebreaker-doubleheader |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

