道奇隊因為在正規賽季對戰落磯隊的成績較佳，因此他們取得這場比賽的[[主場優勢|主場優勢]]。落磯隊派出[[赫曼·馬奎茲|赫曼·馬奎茲]]先發，而道奇隊的先發投手則是[[沃克·布勒|沃克·布勒]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Kelly |first=Matt |url=https://www.mlb.com/news/mlb-playoff-picture-update/c-293413208 |title=MLB Playoff Picture Update |publisher=MLB.com |date=2018-05-24 |access-date=2018-10-01 |archive-date=2019-02-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190208110549/https://www.mlb.com/news/mlb-playoff-picture-update/c-293413208 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。這場比賽的電視轉播是由[[ESPN|ESPN]]負責，播報員包括{{le|喬恩·沙姆比|Jon Sciambi}}、[[大衛·羅斯|大衛·羅斯]]和{{le|里克·沙克里夫|Rick Sutcliffe}}。此外，廣播轉播也由[[ESPN廣播|ESPN廣播]]負責，播報員有{{le|亞當·阿敏|Adam Amin}}和{{le|吉姆·鮑登|Jim Bowden}}<ref>{{cite web |last=Cafardo |first=Ben |url=https://espnmediazone.com/us/press-releases/2018/09/espn-to-exclusively-televise-both-mlb-national-league-tiebreaker-games-on-monday/ |title=ESPN To Exclusively Televise Both MLB National League Tiebreaker Games On Monday - ESPN MediaZone U.S |publisher=Espnmediazone.com |date=2018-09-30 |access-date=2018-10-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181002214909/https://espnmediazone.com/us/press-releases/2018/09/espn-to-exclusively-televise-both-mlb-national-league-tiebreaker-games-on-monday/ |archive-date=2018-10-02 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://blogs.hudsonvalley.com/hudson-valley-sports-tv/2018/09/30/espn-espn-radio-have-coverage-of-mondays-baseball-playoffs/ |title=ESPN, ESPN Radio have coverage of Monday’s baseball playoffs |publisher=Blogs.hudsonvalley.com |date=2018-09-30 |access-date=2018-10-07 |archive-date=2021-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108235341/http://blogs.hudsonvalley.com/hudson-valley-sports-tv/2018/09/30/espn-espn-radio-have-coverage-of-mondays-baseball-playoffs/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

落磯隊先發投手馬奎茲雖然主投{{frac|4|2|3}}局就送出九次三振，但在四局下半和五局分下半分別遭到[[科迪·貝林傑|科迪·貝林傑]]及[[麥克斯·蒙西|麥克斯·蒙西]]狙擊，各挨一發二分彈後退場<ref name=mlb.com/>。而與此同時，道奇隊先發的布勒前五局卻演出無安打，即便主投完{{frac|6|2|3}}也僅被敲一支安打。落磯隊一直到九局上半才突破封鎖，靠著[[諾蘭·阿里納多|諾蘭·阿里納多]]及[[崔佛·史托瑞|崔佛·史托瑞]]兩人從[[肯利·簡森|肯利·簡森]]手中各擊出一支陽春砲追回兩分。即便如此，落磯隊整場比賽還是僅敲出四支[[安打|安打]]<ref>{{cite web |last=Newman |first=Kyle |url=https://www.denverpost.com/2018/10/01/rockies-offense-no-shows-dodgers-nl-west-tiebreaker/ |title=Too little, too late performance by Rockies' offense dooms NL West title hopes |publisher=Denverpost.com |access-date=2018-10-02 |archive-date=2021-01-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210108151952/https://www.denverpost.com/2018/10/01/rockies-offense-no-shows-dodgers-nl-west-tiebreaker/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最終讓道奇隊以5比2獲勝，在[[國聯西區|國聯西區]]六連霸。道奇隊成為史上第三支分區六連霸的球隊（史上第一支是1991年至2005年間在[[國聯東區|國聯東區]]連霸的[[亞特蘭大勇士隊|亞特蘭大勇士隊]]），也是自[[紐約洋基隊|紐約洋基隊]]在1995年至2007年間13連霸[[美聯東區|美聯東區]]以來的首支球隊<ref name=mlb.com>{{cite web|url=https://www.mlb.com/dodgers/news/dodgers-claim-nl-west-title-in-tiebreaker/c-296822024|title=LA wins 6th straight NL West title in tiebreaker|first=Ken|last=Gurnick|work=mlb.com|date=2018-10-01|access-date=2018-10-01|archive-date=2018-12-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20181215080012/https://www.mlb.com/dodgers/news/dodgers-claim-nl-west-title-in-tiebreaker/c-296822024|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==後續==
道奇隊這場比賽獲勝後，以國聯第二種子身分晉級季後賽，並在[[2018年國家聯盟分區賽|國聯分區賽]]中以三勝一敗的戰績擊敗[[亞特蘭大勇士隊|亞特蘭大勇士隊]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.ajc.com/sports/baseball/breaking-braves-will-play-dodgers-nlds/kJbp1eJWP58oCR76AG4DjM/|title=Braves will play Dodgers in NLDS|access-date=2018-11-26|archive-date=2021-01-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210107155625/https://www.ajc.com/sports/baseball/breaking-braves-will-play-dodgers-nlds/kJbp1eJWP58oCR76AG4DjM/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。道奇隊之後在[[2018年國家聯盟冠軍賽|國聯冠軍賽]]裡，與釀酒人隊苦戰七場後勝出<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/25037833/mlb-end-los-angeles-dodgers-talent-trumps-milwaukee-brewers-moves |title=MLB - In the end, Los Angeles Dodgers' talent trumps Milwaukee Brewers' moves |publisher=Espn.com |date=2018-10-21 |access-date=2018-11-26 |archive-date=2021-01-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210111003337/https://www.espn.com/mlb/story/_/id/25037833/mlb-end-los-angeles-dodgers-talent-trumps-milwaukee-brewers-moves |dead-url=no }}</ref>，成功打入[[2018年世界大賽|世界大賽]]，但最終以一勝四敗負於[[波士頓紅襪隊|波士頓紅襪隊]]，無緣奪冠<ref>{{cite web |author=Ted Berg, USA TODAY Sports |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/2018/10/28/red-sox-win-world-series-championship-beat-dodgers/1803801002/ |title=World Series: Red Sox beat Dodgers to win fourth title in 15 years |publisher=Usatoday.com |access-date=2018-11-26 |archive-date=2021-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210110030846/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/2018/10/28/red-sox-win-world-series-championship-beat-dodgers/1803801002/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

而落磯隊這場落敗後以外卡第二的資格晉級季後賽，他們隔天在[[2018年國家聯盟外卡晉級賽|外卡晉級賽]]中擊敗[[芝加哥小熊隊|芝加哥小熊隊]]，但最後在國聯分區賽被釀酒人隊橫掃出局<ref>{{cite web |url=https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/rockies/2018/10/01/rockies-nl-west-mlb-playoffs-wild-card/1494334002/ |title=MLB playoffs: Rockies switch gears for wild-card showdown with Cubs |publisher=Usatoday.com |date=2018-07-19 |access-date=2018-10-02 |archive-date=2020-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201223053132/https://www.usatoday.com/story/sports/mlb/rockies/2018/10/01/rockies-nl-west-mlb-playoffs-wild-card/1494334002/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

